# mkAttPopup w name att
#
# Create a dialog box change current attribute 
#
# Arguments:
#    w -	Name to use for new top-level window.
#    att  -   	Current Att 
#    mode - 	Disable events in other windows ?
# Original author unknown, probably someone at USACERL 1996
